UNITED STATES of America v. CONCHO SAND & GRAVEL COMPANY, Inc. No. 3362. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 26, 1946. Charles E. Dierker, U. S. Atty., and Robert E. Shelton, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellant. A. E. Pearson, of Oklahoma City, Okl., and Hamilton & Kane, of Pawhuska, Old., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal docketed and dismissed pursuant to stipulation.
